1	Research study on Factor 1 (leading questions) — procedure, key terms	AO1
2	Findings of Loftus & Palmer with link to question	AO1
3	Research study on Factor 2 (post-event discussion) — Gabbert et al.	AO1
4	Limitation — ecological validity, elaborated and linked	AO3
5	Limitation — individual differences, research evidence, linked	AO3
6	Counterargument/strength — real-world applications, linked	AO3
